  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">secondment of staff from SOA/PR China to IOC/OOS</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Under the direct supervision of the Head of Section, Ocean Observations and Services, the Assistant Programme Specialist seconded by SOA will be responsible for assisting in matters related to GOOS and JCOMM.

Specifically:
	
&#x2022;	Support development of GOOS and JCOMM databases with a systems view
&#x2022;	Support work of GRAs
&#x2022;	Contribute to development of websites
&#x2022;	Support the technical secretariat of JCOMM Services and Forecasting Systems Programme Area teams
&#x2022;	Conduct and contribute to outreach, communication, and Capacity Development activities, and
&#x2022;	Additional activities for ocean observations and services at IOC, such as the IOC governing body sessions.</narrative>
  </description>
